        "type": "tool_result",
        "content": "Web search results for query: \"AI coding tools changelog \"February 2026\" week 3 week 4\"\n\nI'll perform a web search for AI coding tools changelogs from February 2026, specifically weeks 3 and 4.\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"2026年2月｜AI大模型狂飙19天\",\"url\":\"https://www.toutiao.com/w/1857618754847756/\"},{\"title\":\"2026 年最佳AI 编码工具完全指南 - 稀土掘金\",\"url\":\"https://juejin.cn/post/7606555195754577920\"},{\"title\":\"AI周报2.9：Codex 应用发布，Opus更新4.6 本期盘点 2026 年 2 月第 2 周 AI 圈大事件。OpenAI 推出 macOS 版 Codex 应用并发布 GPT-5.3 编程模型，Apple Xcode 正式集成 Claude，国产视频生成模型可灵 3.0 和即梦 2.0 均突破 15 秒连贯生成。无论你是开发者还是内容创作者，本期视频将带你快速了解最新的生产力工具升级与行业风向。\",\"url\":\"https://jingxuan.douyin.com/m/video/7604853802629385524\"},{\"title\":\"Reflections of Claude Code from CHANGELOG\",\"url\":\"https://dev.to/oikon/reflections-of-claude-code-from-changelog-833\"},{\"title\":\"【Vibe Coding】斯坦福最新教程\",\"url\":\"https://news.qq.com/rain/a/20260224A06NX300\"},{\"title\":\"家人们，2025 年编程圈彻底变天了！AI 编程工具早就不是简单补代码，而是能自主搞定复杂项目的 “开发搭子”。今天这 5 款封神级 AI 编程工具，不管是新手入门还是资深开发，用了直接省出一半时间，快收藏起来～ 第一款 Augment Code，从2022发布开始,直到2025 年的当下,一直是最火的全能选手,AI编程界的\\\"杠把子\\\"！自带超强上下文引擎，能吃透整个代码库，不管是本地还是云端项目都能精准适配。自主编程 Agent 能从头到尾规划任务、自动建 PR，还支持 100 + 外部工具调用，甚至能在终端直接运行命令，团队协作和个人开发都适配。 第二款 Cursor，升级后自然语言转代码精准度拉满！复杂算法、多语言混合编码都能秒生成，错误修复会给多种优化方案，还能实时对接 IDE（VS Code、JetBrains 都支持）。新手跟着它学代码逻辑，进阶速度直接翻倍，老程序员用它省出查资料的时间。 第三款 Trae AI，全栈开发的梦中情 “具”！输入需求就能从前端页面到后端接口完成 0 到 1 搭建，实时解答技术难题不用翻论坛。2025 新增项目模板库，电商网站、管理系统等常见场景直接套用，修改参数就能快速上线，小白也能做出专业级项目。 第四款阿里千问（Qwen3-Coder），开源界的六边形战士！采用 MoE 混合专家架构，480B 总参数加持，原生支持 256K 上下文（可扩展至 1M）。Agent 能力直接媲美顶级模型，多步骤长任务能自主规划，代码生成、补全、修 Bug 样样精通，编程效率从数小时骤降到数分钟。 第五款豆包编程助手，新手和多场景开发必入！创作、问答双模式超实用，上传参考图或画草图就能还原设计生成网页。支持 30 + 编程语言，调试时粘贴报错秒出修复方案，还能实现数据可视化、交互报告制作，零基础也能搞定专业级编程成果。 2025 年的 AI 编程工具早已不是辅助，而是能帮你扛任务、省时间的核心队友。这 5 款都是实测好用的顶流，赶紧码住，下次开发直接开挂！ 关注我,下期我们直接开讲如何使用ai编程工具,开发完整可用项目.\",\"url\":\"https://m.douyin.com/share/video/7565450424800398602\"},{\"title\":\"“AI 在一线：开发人员如何重塑软件开发流程” ｜圆桌讨论\",\"url\":\"https://www.163.com/dy/article/KKM4CI6E0511D3QS.html\"},{\"title\":\"AI development companion for product teams\",\"url\":\"https://www.jetbrains.com/zh-cn/lp/matter/\"},{\"title\":\"2026年AI工具大洗牌：10大AI工具让企业降本增效直接翻倍！\",\"url\":\"https://m.blog.csdn.net/ai979290/article/details/157214463\"},{\"title\":\"2026 年 1月 8 日 随笔档案-疯狂的代码!博客园\",\"url\":\"https://www.cnblogs.com/jjj666/p/archive/2026/01/08\"}]\n\n## Search Results: AI Coding Tools Changelog - February 2026\n\nBased on the search results, here are the key AI coding tool updates and changelog information for **February 2026**:\n\n### Major AI Coding Tool Releases (February 2026)\n\n**Week 3-4 Timeline:**\n\n| Date | Tool | Key Updates |\n|------|------|-------------|\n| **Feb 5** | **Claude Opus 4.6** | Major code capability & tool calling upgrades |\n| **Feb 5** | **GPT-5.3-Codex** | Focused on code generation with comprehensive speed improvements |\n| **Feb 12** | **MiniMax M2.5** | Open-source model with enhanced coding capabilities |\n| **Feb 16** | **Qwen 3.5 (通义千问)** | High cost-performance ratio, focused on agent capabilities |\n| **Feb 17** | **Claude Sonnet 4.6** | Accelerated code processing & long-text reasoning |\n| **Feb 17** | **Fujitsu AI Dev Platform** | Full software development automation |\n| **Feb 19-20** | **Gemini 3.1 Pro** | Stronger code capabilities, more stable agents, longer context |\n\n### Key Trends in February 2026:\n\n1. **Workflow Integration Focus**: 2026 marks the core shift from \"chat windows\" to \"workflow integration\" - AI tools are now deeply integrated throughout the entire development lifecycle\n\n2. **Comprehensive Coverage**: Tools now handle:\n   - Repository reading\n   - Test writing\n   - PR review\n   - CI/CD operations\n\n3. **Agent-Based Development**: 85% of developers regularly use AI tools, with the focus shifting from \"Can it generate code?\" to \"How does it fit into my team's workflow and production constraints?\"\n\n4. **IDE Integration**: Major improvements in AI IDE capabilities, including context management and code understanding enhancements\n\n5. **Multi-step Planning**: Enhanced capabilities for autonomous planning and handling complex, multi-step programming tasks\n\n### Notable Mentions:\n- **Stanford's CS146S course** on modern software development covers AI IDE patterns and agent integration in Weeks 3-4\n- **Physical AI** gaining more attention in 2026\n- Apple Xcode officially integrated Claude during this period\n\nThe search results show February 2026 was a particularly active month for AI coding tool releases, especially during weeks 3-4, with major updates from OpenAI, Anthropic, Google, and Chinese AI companies.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."
